{"tid":1142760,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【大不如前】先達舖68萬沽 五年勁蝕逾六成","createTime":"2019-05-07T09:43:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-09T14:27:49.000Z","uid":75969,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"e76f2c70367f74ef34a62fb5e932b7a55fbe64b0","tid":1142760,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T09:43:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/fin/20190507/s00011/b0758d43ba1cfcbfa4b648f944538bfe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Ffin%2F20190507%2Fs00011%2Fb0758d43ba1cfcbfa4b648f944538bfe.jpg&h=9f5ab8bc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\niPhone炒賣情況今非昔比，令電話集散地、旺角先達廣場身價大不如前，土地註冊處資料顯示，先達廣場2樓一個舖位，上月以68萬元售出，原業主於2013年底以181.8萬元購入，持貨5年多後轉手，帳面蝕約113.8萬元，蝕幅62%，料為該商場近年蝕幅最大舖位成交。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.mpfinance.com/fin/instantp2.php?node=1557221729890&amp;issue=20190507\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mpfinance.com%2Ffin%2Finstantp2.php%3Fnode%3D1557221729890%26issue%3D20190507&d=BbGirfR5U81eMP64OYU5HCaGrLhPWbn%2F%2Bskqqi57m1s%3D&h=82b96ce8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.mpfinance.com/fin/instantp2.php?node=1557221729890&amp;issue=20190507</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/20/184513_711f3b522a641e5d791b686ce87fbb28.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F20%2F184513_711f3b522a641e5d791b686ce87fbb28.jpg&h=5e48c60c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3aa5bd609eb0bc265f7d9f8341feb7bc3bb957f0","tid":1142760,"uid":152476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T09:46:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28e81daa9c239f0c9ba0a9495a7329cea5f4e2f1","tid":1142760,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T09: